vote.title: Authorize acquisition of a drainage easement containing approximately 3,553 square feet of land from Frank David Mitchell located on Whitaker Avenue near its intersection with Genoa Avenue for the Kings Branch Culvert at Genoa Project - Not to exceed $13,000.00 ($10,000.00, plus closing costs and title expenses not to exceed $3,000.00) - Financing:  Flood Control (D) Fund (2017 General Obligation Bond Fund)
